  "texts": [
    "Pd-Mpc's use of MPC ensures that it is able to accomplish this goal without requiring the regulatory authority to reveal the locations of all the drones in the city to the citizen.However, naïve use of MPC in this setting presents scalability problems.",
    "Regulatory authorities operate at a city-scale, possibly tracking hundreds of delivery drones at any given time.",
    "Several thousand citizens may also simultaneously query the regulatory authority to identify drones in their vicinity.",
    "Off-the-shelf MPC protocols are computationally expensive and will have difficulty operating with the number of drones that one may expect at a city-scale.",
    "Moreover, each citizen communicates with the regulatory authority with their mobile phone, and traditional MPC protocols consume significant network bandwidth."
  ],
